jobs_results.description:
Exciting career opportunity to be involved in Digital projects as part of the digital transformation journey of a progressive financial organization.

Mandatory Skill(s)
• At least 1 year of working experience as a Business Analyst or in similar capacity;
• Proficient in gathering, analyzing and documenting requirements from business users;
• Proficient in translating and communicating user requirements in technical terms;
• Experience in coordinating User Acceptance Testing;
• Experience in stakeholder and vendor management;
• Able to work independently, yet a good team player;
• Strong written and oral communication skills.

Desirable Skill(s)
• Prior experience in Insurance or Banking domain;
• SCRUM Certification.

Responsibilities
• Responsible as a liaison between business users and technology team;
• Responsible for managing requirements of Portal / Front end / Mobile / Digital systems projects;
• Understand and analyze user requirements thoroughly;
• Develop functional and... technical specifications for the technical team;
• Conduct business requirements walk through on enhancements / implementation with users and key stakeholders;
• Analyse feasibility and prioritization of business requirements, evaluate the alternative high level technical solutions;
• Define high level business process model and decompose into fine grain activities and tasks;
• Monitor project status and support project manager in giving solutions to resolve problems
